caption: Set Contents
doc: Overwrites editor with given contents. Contents should end with a newline. Returns a Delta representing the change. This will be the same as the Delta passed in, if given Delta had no invalid operations

AAa.caption: Contents (Delta)
AAa.doc: Delta is the way Quill stores the text and formatting you type into the editor. It's like a special code that keeps track of everything you do, like adding or deleting text, changing colors or fonts, and more.
AAa.name: contents
